title: 2021 NEW YEAR’S EVE COUNTDOWN DRONE LIGHT SHOW in YEONGDONG-DAERO (SEOUL)
author: HyundaiWorldwide
description:
We had to put aside everything we dreamed of in 2020.
This pause in our lives was only a short break to leap even higher.
 
And now we take the next step for a tomorrow full of new dreams, greeting the new year, 2021.
Happy New Year for all.

#newyeareve #newyear #drone #droneshow#happynewyear #countdown #2021

localize.description:
2020年，我们不得不抛开一切梦想。
我们生活中的这一停顿只是一个短暂的休息，可以跳得更高。

现在，我们为充满新梦想的明天迈出下一步，迎接新的一年，2021年。
祝大家新年快乐。
